<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 03 at 4:09PM EST  by NWS Raleigh</headline>
<description>...Areas of Black Ice Expected to Develop Tonight...
Lingering areas of snow, slush and runoff on roadways and sidewalks
will likely freeze tonight as temperatures fall well below freezing.
Black ice will be hard to see on highways and sidewalks. Use
caution if traveling tonight and Tuesday morning as slippery
conditions are expected.</description>
